ingredients reqd:-
2 slices of bread
egg
slami 
butter
letuce 
salt and peper 
procedure:-
heat a pan with butter 
put the bread in the butter and flip after 2 mins then off
take your letuce and build a base
in your pan make and omlet or poach(suggested) and when crispy on side place on letuce 
fry your slamis in butter and make it as you wish 
then place and spread some more letuce with salt and peper place the bread over and a toothpick 
done enjoy 
